 agent succeeded once. It doesn'\\\\''t mean it succeeds every time.\\n\\nThe fix isn'\\\\''t slowing down. It'\\\\''s testing differently:\\n→ Run the same scenario multiple times\\n→ Vary phrasing and context\\n→ Inject tool failures\\n→ Turn every production incident into a permanent regression test\\n\\nRepeatability is the metric that matters. Not capability — consistency.\\n\\nYour agent can do the job once. Can it do it a thousand times without breaking?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #Testing #EnterpriseAI #Reliability'\\n\\n/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh 264468965 image /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/boring-agents-1783699220.png \\\"$POST_TEXT\\\"\", \"timeout\": 60}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783799714348,"responseId":"op9SapDRK9_NwOYPvefa4Ak"}}
